Cell C has been awarded the Overall Telecommunications Industry Award in the 2018/2019 Ask Afrika Orange Index. The index uses a survey to measure service excellence across South African companies, said Cell C. The Ask Afrika Orange Index measured 168 companies across 31 industries. “The accolade comes as a result of the company’s customer-first values and strategy that are driven daily by the dedicated staff at Cell C,” it said. Cell C’s Chief Customer Experience Officer Michelle Beetar said customer service is a critical driver of success in the telecommunications industry. “I’d like to extend our heartfelt thanks to everyone on the Cell C team for the enduringly high levels of professionalism they demonstrate on a daily basis and for always putting the customer first,” said Beetar.